{"tid":628090,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【四月新番】奴隸區 我與 23 個奴隸","createTime":"2018-04-13T13:44:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-24T10:13:39.000Z","uid":135110,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"a85edc9db336e3015195fa0f28824fe750a9bdde","tid":628090,"uid":135110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T13:44:47.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/13/214351_3b469f06927bcc37b4259c5781a54d3b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F13%2F214351_3b469f06927bcc37b4259c5781a54d3b.png&h=045a98a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《奴隸區 我與 23 個奴隸》描述名為「SCM」的產品，把此器具裝在上顎內側進行對決，敗者就淪為奴隸。由 24 位主角所展開的慾望殊死戰，金錢、復仇、愛情，最後的贏家到底是誰。乍看之下相當簡單的規則，會誘發人性走向無法想像的邪惡面。<br />\n■ STAFF <br />\n原作：大石普人、岡田伸一<br />\n監督：倉谷涼一<br />\n角色設計：後藤潤二<br />\n音樂：長田直之<br />\n動畫製作：ZERO-G&times;TNK<br />\n<br />\n■ CAST <br />\n荒川英愛：山村響<br />\n大田優牙：鈴木崚汰<br />\n葛飾授理愛：千本木彩花<br />\n新宿星矢：綠川光<br />\n豐島絢香：木下鈴奈<br />\n<br />\n■ INFO <br />\n放送日期：4 月 12 日 <br />\n每週更新：星期五</div>"},{"pid":"2d8da79ce567fca9ca8f98c8605b0324d2cafe44","tid":628090,"uid":135110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T13:44:55.000Z","msg":"PV:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G3tmg52yPxA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DG3tmg52yPxA&d=NLRT3BKytKoMD2lY%2F%2BqSXi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=a61b74c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G3tmg52yPxA</a>"},{"pid":"4ade3ffbda47ce982e25ec695cf020e6a1c82539","tid":628090,"uid":135110,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T14:19:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/13/221924_00a916801868f5a2cbf025a11520a3b6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F13%2F221924_00a916801868f5a2cbf025a11520a3